# Prefer the native OS shell

When proposing commands, **prefer the user's native OS shell**:

- **Windows**: PowerShell (`pwsh`/`powershell`) syntax (no bash heredocs)
- **macOS/Linux**: bash/zsh syntax

If a command needs different quoting/escaping across shells, provide the **PowerShell version first** on Windows and avoid shell-specific constructs unless necessary.
